(38486, '9B4655A7-A0EA-49C6-AFD1-F56F33D2E640', 'A few moments I am thankful for with you in the last day (or so) Your 24 egg salad triumph The moment I saw you in the kitchen looking stunning in your  aqua branch dress  Pulling me aside in the agam room to prepare me for my talk with Jonah Your photo then pit stop then assessment of the fudge….mediocre Your artichoke heart triumph (signature dish) Wake up Scratches across my chest Your thanksgiving table talk…”what are you thankful for?” I could list one thing I’m thankful for for each calorie I consumed last night. It would be a long list. But the first thousand calories would be dedicated to how thankful I am for you. I love you so much….. thank you for making these moments and so many more, ones that I can replay and double and triple my joy. You make each 24 hours a new day in an incredible adventure together. I am the luckiest person on earth. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2021-11-26T05:51:20.317900'),
