(38636, '06DAF89C-1EAB-492E-A94F-0A4727ACB836', 'Dear love, isn’t it the best waking up well rested next to you to then send our delightful child to school? Yes it is. Thank you for helping make the week truly wonderful. I know it was a lot for you and appreciate how you fully engaged and made it enjoyable for all of us. And a random image I am savoring…how carved and hot you looked on the bed yesterday from behind….when I touched and kissed your shoulder  blade. Funny what sets the mind (and body off) with charges…I get them from you all the time.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2021-11-29T09:31:03.483000'),
(38637, '958F5FC8-75AB-4C16-B35B-316ABCBAEB6F', '￼Chilly', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2021-11-29T10:03:09.622339'),
(38640, '7DCA1FC9-6A17-4ED6-A1C9-DA6472E82BF5', 'To my love love. I️ often times find myself just thinking about how good the simplest things in life feel with you - crawling in bed and wrapping my legs around you while resting and recovering from an early morning flight. How much your presence and your body enwrapped in mine is the surest bet towards feeling completely calm, and also so sweetly happy at the same time.  I️ revel in the delight of ending my days with you - debriefing the ins and outs from the day and happy moments that come from something Orli has said or done and then once again falling asleep touching your body. So simple and yet, I️ don’t take any of it for granted. You’re my rock and there is so much joy in the simplicity of living life together. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2021-11-29T11:38:10.837579'),
(38641, 'F3AC8072-8EDE-42B6-A52A-F584B7CA055E', 'I️ know that this last week was a lot. It was high anxiety knowing that I️ was feeling really unenthusiastic about this trip and you hoping that it would be peaceful. I️t’s hard being in between my levels of discomfort and also wanting things to work well with your family. I️’m happy it went better than either of us planned for it to go and the cousins could play and frolic. It was equally fun for me to watch lucy and Orli enjoy each other so very much. Thank you for balancing the difficult tight rope of supporting me through that reasonable and yet high anxiety space while also engaging with your family. You are calm and even and it takes down the drama. I️ appreciate that deeply about you. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2021-11-29T11:41:19.456483'),
(38642, 'CA8CA158-D3E9-4881-8544-BB5AB553F1A5', 'And lastly, I️ really appreciated you being so present with us and our family and giving me the sense of comfort that you and Ilsa were taking a few days off to be with me and the boys and Orli. You are also managing a tight rope of enjoying the fun of connecting and playing with someone else, while also making me feel loved and valued in the deepest way. Your heartfelt notes are really meaningful and so is all your IRL affection. You are pulling off something that is incredibly hard. This is a team valiant efforts and I️’m grateful. I️ see your hard work and it makes me just love you harder and harder every day. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2021-11-29T11:47:08.236824'),
