(38859, 'F7A15BAF-A66C-49F0-957F-AE1B91CD94A6', 'I’ll refrain from saying its your job to manage your emotions. I understand that this whole experiment has been a lot for you to take in and I’m grateful to you for working so hard primarily for my benefit…although ultimately for both of us. Understanding better what made you feel unsafe and why made it easier for me to see how and why I needed to shift and become more conscious of some of my own behaviors. You were not crazy for feeling how you were feeling. But I don’t feel comfortable if your take away is that the reason you were feeling this way was because I’m out of control….and that this is just another repeat of Amy. It’s not, and I’m not. I didn’t understand your needs and it took a while for you to get to place where you could communicate what was under the surface,  so I could empathize, internalize my role….how I could help you…. and then change. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2021-12-01T14:23:23.445000'),
